 "lrc": "[00:00.00]You asked why it feels like night today\n[00:00.00]I was the one who dimmed the room\n[00:00.00]You asked what wasn’t right today\n[00:00.00]I was already moving through you\n[00:00.00]Cut—cut—cut you\n[00:00.00]You asked why the night came early\n[00:32.72]I pulled the shade across the sky\n[00:34.32]You asked what felt wrong inside you\n[00:37.60]I was teaching fear to lie\n[00:40.56]You asked why your chest stayed tightened\n[00:42.24]I kept my hand around the thread\n[00:44.96]You didn’t know what stressed you first\n[00:46.96]I fed the pressure in your head\n[00:49.76]You know what the voice feels like\n[00:51.20]Because I learned how to speak low\n[00:52.64]In the back of every thought\n[00:53.76]Where the quiet things grow\n[00:55.04]I’m the face that you hold inside\n[00:56.40]I wake up when your eyes close\n[00:57.68]I watch every little lie\n[00:58.72]And laugh when your balance goes\n[00:59.84]I see everything\n[01:01.68]Every crack you hide within\n[01:04.24]When it’s time to sink or swim\n[01:06.40]I breathe right under your skin\n[01:09.68]You keep looking back\n[01:11.28]But I was never far behind\n[01:14.40]You keep hearing storms\n[01:16.08]Because I spin them in your mind\n[01:20.48]I know why you’re paranoid\n[01:22.56]I’m the shadow at your back\n[01:24.48]I know why your head keeps spinning\n[01:27.28]I’m the wind inside the static\n[01:29.60]I know why you hear me within\n[01:31.12]I’m the voice you can’t undo\n[01:33.52]I know why the face is near\n[01:36.80]I’m the paper that cut you\n[01:39.60]Cut you\n[01:40.32]Cut you\n[01:41.84]Paper that cut you\n[01:43.60]Still beneath\n[01:44.32]Still beneath\n[01:46.08]Still beneath your skin\n[01:47.84]You said you’ve got a face in you\n[01:49.04]I know, I carved it carefully\n[01:50.24]Pointing out mistakes to you\n[01:51.36]Was the way I made you carry me\n[01:52.64]You said we all have one inside\n[01:53.84]Now you’re finally speaking true\n[01:54.96]But the face you fear in everyone\n[01:56.24]Is learning tricks from you\n[01:57.28]You asked what set you off first\n[01:59.04]I was there before the spark\n[02:00.32]You asked why you can’t stand it\n[02:01.52]I was whispering in the dark\n[02:02.72]They act like you don’t measure up\n[02:04.16]So I sharpen every doubt\n[02:05.36]I turn every little comparison\n[02:06.88]Into something you can’t get out\n[02:08.48]Everybody has a face inside\n[02:10.00]A watcher in the wires\n[02:10.64]A witness when the truth gets bent\n[02:12.96]A laugh beneath the fire\n[02:16.80]So when they sink or swim\n[02:18.88]They’ll feel what you’ve been through\n[02:20.40]The face inside is watching them\n[02:23.68]The way I watched you too\n[02:26.56]You keep looking back\n[02:28.00]But I was never far behind\n[02:31.12]You keep hearing storms\n[02:32.72]Because I spin them in your mind\n[02:36.48]I know why you’re paranoid\n[02:38.24]I’m the shadow at your back\n[02:41.28]I know why your head keeps spinning\n[02:43.28]I’m the wind inside the static\n[02:46.08]I know why you hear me within\n[02:48.88]I’m the voice you can’t undo\n[02:50.16]I know why the face is near\n[02:52.56]I’m the paper that cut you\n[02:56.72]The cut is right beneath your skin\n[03:00.64]The cut is right beneath your skin\n[03:04.48]The cut is right beneath your skin\n[03:06.72]When the sun goes down\n[03:14.56]I’m the reason light feels guilty\n[03:18.24]When the sun goes down\n[03:19.87]I make the daylight turn against you\n[03:23.36]When the sun goes down\n[03:26.08]I’m the grin behind the evening\n[03:27.84]When the sun goes down\n[03:29.23]I make the mirror sing back to you\n[03:35.25]You asked who was watching\n[03:39.84]You were\n[03:40.58]You asked what was laughing\n[03:42.64]You were\n[03:42.91]You asked why it followed\n[03:45.43]You moved\n[03:46.78]You asked what was inside\n[03:49.44]Not you\n[03:49.84]You don’t sing me\n[03:50.60]I remix you\n[03:51.28]Cut you\n[03:51.91]Cut you\n[03:52.33]Paper that cut you\n[03:53.28]I know why you’re paranoid\n[04:04.40]I’m the shadow at your back\n[04:07.52]I know why your head keeps spinning\n[04:09.92]I’m the wind inside the static\n[04:12.48]I know why you hear me within\n[04:14.56]I’m the voice you can’t undo\n[04:16.40]I know why the face is near\n[04:19.76]I’m the paper that cut you\n[04:21.28]I know why you’re paranoid\n[04:24.48]I’m the warning in the room\n[04:26.40]I know why the light betrays\n[04:28.96]I was standing next to you\n[04:30.80]I know why you can’t stop hearing\n[04:34.40]What I buried deep within\n[04:35.60]I know why the face is near\n[04:39.12]I’m still beneath your skin\n[04:41.44]You asked why it feels like night today\n[04:47.20]Now you know\n[04:51.28]You asked what wasn’t right today\n[04:54.32]Now you know\n[04:54.32]Cut—cut—cut you\n[04:54.32]Good night\n"
